$(" #modal11 ").click( function (){
		$("#modal1").html( " <h2>The Congratulator</h2>	<hr class=\"smallb\"><p class=\"item-intro text-muted\">Small Website</p> <hr class=\"congratu\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"congra-f\">The Congratulator was created in order to to bless my family and friends for the jewish new year - \"Rosh Hashana\".</div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img class=\"img-responsive congra-pic\" src=\"img/portfolio/congra1.png\"></div></div><hr class=\"congratu\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6 hidden-md hidden-lg congra\" style=\"margin-top:50px\"><div >At first, I wrote it for my own use - something to send to my relatives before the holiday. After finishing writing it, I thought - \"Hey, why not offer anyone who also wants a congratulator to create one?\", So I made a small system to handle users' Congratulators.</div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img class=\"img-responsive congra-pic\" src=\"img/portfolio/congra2.png\"></div><div class=\"col-md-6 hidden-xs hidden-sm\"><div class=\"congra\">At first, I wrote it for my own use - something to send to my relatives before the holiday. After finishing writing it, I thought - \"Hey, why not offer anyone who also wants a congratulator to create one?\", So I made a small system to handle users' customisable Congratulators.</div></div></div><hr class=\"congratu\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"congra congra-m\">How was the website built?<br>I used Javascript and jQuery for the typewriter effect and forms handling on client side.<br>Users system was created using PHP and MySQL.</div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\" align=\"center\"><img class=\"img-responsive congra-pic\" src=\"img/portfolio/congra3.png\"></div>	</div><br><a href=\"http://www.eilon.me/\" target=\"_blank\"><button class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\">Visit The Congratulator</button></a><br><br>	<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-dismiss=\"modal\"><i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i> Close</button>" );
	});
	
$(" #modal22 ").click( function (){
	$("#modal2").html("	<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"css/jquery.fancybox.css?v=2.1.5\" media=\"screen\" /><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 logs-mod-con\"><h2 style=\"color: #fff\">Logs and Ropes</h2><hr class=\"small\"><div class=\"logs-text\">In my childhood, I took part in my hometown's scouts branch.<br>Each summer, we used to go on a summer camp together with all the scouts branches in our area.<br><br>The competition between the branches was very intense and there are prizes at the end of the summer camp for the branches that had the best camps.<br>When my friends and I were the ones in charge of building the camp we decided to try new methods of building figures out of logs and ropes.<br><br>We studied on our own how to use SketchUp, Google's architecture software and after many trials and errors, we succeeded in turning digital sketches into 18 feet figures.<br><br>Here are some photos of the process: (Click to enlarge)<br><br></div><p><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/1.png\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tornado digital model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/1_thumb.png\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/2.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tornado - beginning\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/2_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/3.JPG\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tornado - starting to gain height\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/3_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/4.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tornado - ready!\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/4_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/5.JPG\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tornado and its small scale model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/5_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/6.png\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Lion digital model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/6_thumb.png\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/7.JPG\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Lion - ready\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/7_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/8.png\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tinman digital model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/8_thumb.png\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/9.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tinman - half way there...\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/9_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/10.JPG\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tinman - almost done\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/10_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/11.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Tinman - ready\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/11_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/12.JPG\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Zapdos Pokemon - small scale model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/12_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/13.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Zapdos - ready\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/13_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/13_1.png\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Monkey - digital model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/13_1_thumb.png\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/14.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Monkey head\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/14_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" href=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/15.png\" data-fancybox-group=\"gallery\" title=\"Digital model\"><img src=\"img/portfolio/logsnro/15_thumb.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></p><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px\" data-dismiss=\"modal\"><i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i> Close</button></div></div>");
